{"tid":55252,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［直播］Boxing Day自製好味煮水餃","createTime":"2016-12-26T09:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T08:38:59.000Z","uid":35639,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a53a2af076316b18d37c56eb9eb2d2c8e901b54","tid":55252,"uid":35639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T09:08:46.000Z","msg":"前回提要s<br />\n［直播］平安夜自製攬女鋸和牛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/52918/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/52918/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n［直播］聖誕夜自製毒撚辣雞麵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/54351/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/54351/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n首先講返尋晚臨訓小插曲先<br />\n話說毒撚最怕凍<br />\n又無女攬<br />\n於是想整返個暖水袋暖笠笠咁瞓覺<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/26/170628_83bbe6c471c38836c50a539275195130.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F26%2F170628_83bbe6c471c38836c50a539275195130.jpg&h=3c6fad9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有用過呢款暖水袋都知<br />\n呢個蓋真係好難開<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F81Nj8s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF81Nj8s.jpg&h=cbfe1e5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但我用盡九牛二虎之力<br />\n終於。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/26/170750_1bdd0ef6e39a56eaea7dde2dd825c539.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F26%2F170750_1bdd0ef6e39a56eaea7dde2dd825c539.jpg&h=5c02ede5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果都係用唔到凍住咁瞓。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返正題<br />\n今次材料<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/26/170842_dc8e68933c294b45d0ef0511a98f3232.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"ht